A <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Postman_%28film%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Postman_%28film%29" target="_blank">postman</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filmmaking" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filmmaking" target="_blank">filmed</a> himself <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" target="_blank">abusing</a> two <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infant" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infant" target="_blank">babies</a>  including a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infant" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infant" target="_blank">newborn</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" target="_blank">girl</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ageing" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ageing" target="_blank">aged</a> just five weeks oldJohnathan Forshaw claimed he was a &quotsex <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addict</a>&quot after <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_officer" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_officer" target="_blank">police</a> uncovered more than 21000 <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decency" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decency" target="_blank">indecent</a> images of youngsters following his <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arrest" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arrest" target="_blank">arrest</a> last NovemberThey revealed the 33 yearold had preyed on a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiny_Mix_Tapes" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiny_Mix_Tapes" target="_blank">tiny</a> boy and girl The first victim was less than a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" target="_blank">year</a> old when he was attackedThe other had been born just over a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" target="_blank">month</a> earlier when Forshaw first <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_abuse" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_abuse" target="_blank">molested</a> herHe is now behind bars after he admitted a string of charges including <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_assault" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_assault" target="_blank">sexual assault</a> using lewd and libidinous <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Behavior" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Behavior" target="_blank">behaviour</a> and <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Child_pornography" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Child_pornography" target="_blank">child porn</a> offencesPolice swooped at Forshaw's home in Campbeltown Argyll last NovemberOfficers found thousands of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decency" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Decency" target="_blank">indecent</a> images that had been downloaded from <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Website" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Website" target="_blank">websites</a> and via Skype between 2005 and 2014It also emerged that he had <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recording" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recording" target="_blank">recorded</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Footage" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Footage" target="_blank">footage</a> of him <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" target="_blank">abusing</a> childrenA young boy was <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_abuse" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sexual_abuse" target="_blank">molested</a> in the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_of_Sam" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_of_Sam" target="_blank">summer of</a> 2009 He then went on to repeatedly <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/September_11_attacks" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/September_11_attacks" target="_blank">attack</a> a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" target="_blank">little girl</a> between 2011 and last yearThe <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_%28Ireland%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_%28Ireland%29" target="_blank">High Court</a> in <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow" target="_blank">Glasgow</a> was told how she was just weeks old when the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuse" target="_blank">abuse</a> startedDuring the one incident the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Girl" target="_blank">girl</a> is <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amber_Heard" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amber_Heard" target="_blank">heard</a> saying &quotdon't&quot while Forshaw is with herForshaw also <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yesterday_%28song%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yesterday_%28song%29" target="_blank">yesterday</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plea" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plea" target="_blank">pleaded guilty</a> to a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Number" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Number" target="_blank">number</a> of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Voyeurism" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Voyeurism" target="_blank">voyeurism</a> charges He secretly <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recording" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recording" target="_blank">recorded</a> three women visiting his home using the bathroom or while they were partially clothedForshaw also <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filmmaking" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filmmaking" target="_blank">filmed</a> another young girl without her knowledgeAfter being held for the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crime" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crime" target="_blank">crimes</a> Forshaw <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Writing" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Writing" target="_blank">wrote</a> a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Number" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Number" target="_blank">number</a> of letters to his partner and his brother &quotapologising&quot for what went onHe claimed he <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felt_%28band%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felt_%28band%29" target="_blank">felt</a> &quotguilty&quot described himself as a &quotsex <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addiction" target="_blank">addict</a>&quot and that using <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cannabis_%28drug%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cannabis_%28drug%29" target="_blank">cannabis</a> had apparently affected himDonald MacLeod QC defending said Forshaw had shown &quota lot of contrition&quot for what he had doneLord Turnbull deferred sentencing for reports until next <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" target="_blank">month</a>
